articles.title: Ohio weathers late Eastern Michigan rally, earns a 74-68 win
articles.description: ATHENS, Ohio (AP) — Jason Preston hit 3 of 4 from the free throw line in the final 21 seconds and Ohio held off a late rally to beat Eastern Michigan, 74-68 in a Mid-America Conference game on Tuesday night.
articles.content:

articles.title: Arizona congressman criticized after tweeting doctored photo
articles.description: PHOENIX (AP) — Arizona Congressman Paul Gosar is getting criticism after tweeting a doctored picture of former President Barack Obama and Iranian President Hassan Rouhani in which he seemed not to realize the foreign leader remains in power.
